      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ない。ないないないない！　おしゃれなホテルも\n格式高い旅館もお肌すべすべ温泉もどこにもなーい！",
      "startTime": 5.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.2785486857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはそうだよ、お寺なんだもん。ただ、お寺は\nお寺でも普通のお寺じゃないよ、凄まじいお寺だから",
      "startTime": 16.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 21.4452153523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "最近プロレス団体の広告塔になったんだけど、そこで\n仲良くなったタンク岡本さんに教えてもらったんだ",
      "startTime": 25.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.9452140808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "プロレスラーはもちろんのこと、スポーツ選手が精神と\n肉体を鍛え直すためによく修行に入るお寺なんだって",
      "startTime": 34.0666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 38.7452171326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、愛がそういうお仕事してたのは知ってるけど\nなんでプロレス団体御用達のお寺にアイドルが行く訳？",
      "startTime": 42.0000017803,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6221.452585900003,
          "startTime": 44.9666697185
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 46.0233120601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
