        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3776.6909917000007,
          "startTime": 49.8000030518
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.5899759293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "この場所を提案したのは莉央さんで、最近BIG4の\n肩書に調子に乗ってるこころを鍛え直すのが目的だって",
      "startTime": 57.6666656495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 62.6233084997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？　別に調子に乗ってませんけど！\nふさわしい振る舞いしてますけどね。BIG4なんで！",
      "startTime": 65.9666648866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 70.286482811
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……たぶん、冗談でも\nそういうこと言ってるからじゃないかなぁ",
      "startTime": 74.1333315533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 77.5198161443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "きっと先に目的と場所を言うと私が逃げると思って\n{user}さんを口止めしてたんだ！",
      "startTime": 81.6666648866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 84.8359836578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "くぅ～～！　悔しい～！\n莉央さん、全然私のこと理解してな～い！",
      "startTime": 87.4666648866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 91.7757793108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも、こころの頑張りは分かってると思うよ\nそのうえで生活を正すために用意してくれたのかも",
      "startTime": 95.6999982199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、最近こころ、生活リズムが乱れがちで\n夜寝るのも遅いみたいだし……",
      "startTime": 103.6333315533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 106.2757793108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、そ、それは……夜遅くまで友達が貸してくれた\nノートを写したり、読み込んだりしてたからだし",
      "startTime": 111.5666648866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 115.6845314342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "その後寝る前に、みんなに隠れてプリンをいくつか\n食べたりはしてたけど、本当にそれぐらいだし",
      "startTime": 118.7884290058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 122.1311749457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "勉強頑張るのは大事だけど、ちゃんと夜は寝ないと……\nあと深夜のプリンは普通にダメだからね",
      "startTime": 127.0333315533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、合宿でみっちり修行して、生活リズムも直れば\nライブも、もっといい出来になると思うよ",
      "startTime": 135.4999982199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 138.5311749457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても、だとしても……くぅ～～！\n莉央さんの鬼っ！　悪魔～！　すっとこどっこい～！",
      "startTime": 143.3333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 147.3462314287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
