      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 161.9283176103
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 163.8950025873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "ふぎゃーーーー！！ な、何するんですか、住職さん！\nBIG4のこころを木の板で打つだなんて！",
      "startTime": 167.7333407086,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-03.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 163.533342743
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 171.7658413884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "それに縁側で坐禅して瞑想だなんて\nアイドルに必要なことだとは思えないんですけどー……",
      "startTime": 175.8000073752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、す、すぐ瞑想し直しますから！\nその凶悪な木の板をどうかしまって下さーい！",
      "startTime": 183.1666740419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 187.0616910295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_13_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "（精神集中、精神集中～～～～……うー、辛い……）\n（こういう時は、プリンのことでも考えて――）",
      "startTime": 193.8666740419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
